# openSUSE Build Service 2.1.4
#

Updaters from any OBS 2.1 release can just ugrade the packages and restart
all services. Updaters from former releases should read the
README.UPDATERS file.

This release is a security release, fixing the publishing of sources which
have been set to disallow sourceaccess.

Feature backport:
=================

* none

Changes:
========

* none

Bugfixes:
=========

* backend: obey sourcaccess setting when publishing
* backend: fix sourceaccess flags forwarding in source server
* webui: fix crasher for attributes#edit when package doesn't exist

